verbose_text: In parallel, compared with exposure to normoxia, 4 weeks of exposure to IH augmented the O-GlcNAc protein, OGT, phosphorylated ERK1/2 and p38 MAPK levels, accompanied by a decrease in OGA levels and an increase in cardiomyocyte apoptosis, as well as an increase in the levels of caspase-3, NF-kappaB p65, TNF-alpha and IL-6 in the LV tissues (XREF_FIG and XREF_FIG).
